      "value": "<p><em>You're always ready to lend your partner a hand.</em><br /><br /><strong>Prerequisites</strong><br />Bonded Mind.<br /><br /><strong>Benefits</strong><br />When you successfully use the Aid Another action to assist an ally's skill check, and the ally also has this feat, the bonus is +4 instead of +2.</p>\n<p><br /><strong>Pathfinder Society<br /></strong>A PC cannot benefit from the feat Bonded Mind or any teamwork feats that use it as a prerequisite unless he permanently possesses the feat; this is an exception to how an inquisitor's solo tactics ability, a cavalier's tactician ability, and similar abilities function.</p>",
